sentences: Nori Shiraishi (白石 乃梨, Shiraishi Nori, born 9 May 1986) is a Japanese producer, model, singer and songwriter under Giza Studio label.
In 2008 she debuted as a soloist Kikyo Shiraishi, in 2009 changed it into her real name Nori Shiraishi and in 2011 under dancing group Caos Caos Caos.
